data.description:
Rare chance to own a breathtaking Key West-style home with 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, nestled in a private community in the heart of Stuart. Just minutes from Historic Downtown and Stuart Beach. This lovely home was built in 2017 and features quality CBS construction, a stylish metal roof, and full impact glass coverage for added security.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by elegant wood-look porcelain tile floors, soaring ceilings, and attractive, modern finishes throughout. The kitchen offers ample space and features a custom-built center island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a convenient breakfast bar, and a formal dining room. The split floor plan is both spacious and offers plenty of privacy. Complete with a Large Master Suite which is accompanied by a luxurious master bathroom that features his and hers sinks, a separate Roman tub, a large walk-in shower with an additional rain shower stemming from the ceiling, and an extra-large walk-in closet. 

The 2-car garage has beautifully updated floors. The home includes a water filtration system, a new water heater, electric roller shades that cover the back patio slider doors for added convenience, and so much more.

Indulge in endless evenings of relaxation or entertainment on the lanai porch, fully fenced-in and perfect for unwinding or hosting gatherings.

This family-friendly community is located within walking distance to the historic downtown Stuart, nearby marinas, close to dining & shopping, and only a short drive to Stuart Beach. This is one opportunity you don't want to miss.

Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of paradise in Stuart. Schedule your showing today!
